The Look of Love is the sixth album by Canadian jazz pianist and vocalist Diana Krall, released in 2001. It became Diana Krall's best-selling album, best-selling album of Canada and best-selling album of 2001. Billboard ranked album at number 5 on the magazine's Top Jazz Albums of the Decade.
